I don't think you should add 8 to the x position of the right paddle to check for it. Because I believe the ball is supposed to collide with the right edge of the left paddle, in which case you'd add 8 to the X position, and the ball is supposed to collide with the left edge of the right paddle, in which case you wouldn't add anything.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=138">Celius</a> — Thu Jan 29, 2009 3:23 pm</p><hr />
